channel.title: Server wont add to status page?
channel.description: Hey everyone i dont know if this is the right section but.....why wont my server add onto moparscape server status page??i added it 3 days ago and retried yesterday..they just gimmie username and passworld and tell me to wait for it to add...and it still hasnt been added?does anyone know the problem with it? I bought a vps for my server about 4 days ago and servers been on since then still no1 online lmfao.someone please help me with a solution to the moparscape server status page.
